<h3>📦 Installation</h3>
<p>This library requires <a href="https://php.net/releases/" target="_blank">PHP 8.4+</a> and is installed via <a href="https://getcomposer.org/" target="_blank">Composer</a>:</p>
<pre class="language-bash prettyprint">composer require oihana/php-enums</pre>

<h3>✨ Features</h3>
<h4>Reflection helpers</h4>
<ul>
	<li>📦 Multiple enumerations for different domains (e.g. Boolean, Char, IniOptions, and more).</li>
	<li>🔍 Reflection-ready with ConstantsTrait for listing or validating values.</li>
	<li>🛡️ Reduces “magic strings” and improves semantic clarity.</li>
	<li>🧩 Easily reusable in any PHP application or framework.</li>
	<li>⚡ No external dependencies except Oihana’s reflection utilities.</li>
</ul>

<h3>✅ Running Unit Tests</h3>
<pre class="language-bash prettyprint">composer test</pre>
<p>Run a specific test file:</p>
<pre class="language-bash prettyprint">composer test ./tests/oihana/enums/BooleanTest.php</pre>

<h3>🛠️ Generate the API Docs</h3>
<p>We use phpDocumentor to generate the HTML docs into <code>./docs</code>.</p>
<pre class="language-bash prettyprint">composer doc</pre>

